biography:

Ines Montani is a developer specializing in tools for AI and NLP technology. She’s a Fellow of the Python Software Foundation, the co-founder and CEO of [Explosion](https://explosion.ai) and a core developer of [spaCy](https://spacy.io), one of the leading open-source libraries for Natural Language Processing in Python, and [Prodigy](https://prodi.gy), a modern annotation tool for creating training data for machine learning models.
